videos.description: Washington State QB Anthony Gordon airs it out to Travell Harris who makes a great catch for a 35-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Washington State scores early with deep ball

videos.description: Jayden Daniels throws it deep to Brandon Aiyuk who reels in a 40-yard touchdown to get Arizona State on the board

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (ASU's Aiyuk hauls in 40-yard score) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: ASU's Aiyuk hauls in 40-yard score

videos.description: Anthony Gordon throws to a wide-open Dezmon Patmon for a 2-yard score to extend Washington State's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patmon left all alone for Cougars TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Patmon left all alone for Cougars TD

videos.description: Arizona State's Brandon Aiyuk catches a short pass and puts on the burners, speeding away from the Washington State defense for his second score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ayiuk speeds away from defense for 86-yard ASU TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayiuk speeds away from defense for 86-yard ASU TD

videos.description: Arizona State's Eno Benjamin gets the ball and runs through the hole in the line to make the score 24-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (ASU's Benjamin bursts through hole for 32-yard score) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: ASU's Benjamin bursts through hole for 32-yard score

videos.description: Washington State's Anthony Gordon throws a dart to Easop Winton Jr. for a 2-yard score even the score at 24-24.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gordon connects with Winston for TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon connects with Winston for TD

videos.description: Max Borghi takes the handoff and makes his way into the end zone for a two-yard touchdown to put the Cougars up 31-24.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State retakes lead with 2-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State retakes lead with 2-yard TD

videos.description: Arizona State's Brandon Aiyuk blows past a defender and scores a 33-yard touchdown, his third of the game.
